dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is John Harris. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Kimberly. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Of course. It's zero zero two three four one.
Thank you, Kimberly. Additionally, may I have your date of birth in the format of day, month, year?
Sure, it's two eight zero one, June, one nine eight five.
Thank you for that information, Kimberly. How can I assist you today with your Old Stone Auto Insurance policy?
I'd like to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
I can help you with that. Let's go through the details of the vehicle you'd like to add. Is it a car, truck, or motorcycle?
Thank you for your time, Kimberly. I will assist you further with adding the new vehicle to your policy. Have a great day!
